        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-4 font-medium" data-i18n="jose.hero.subtitle">
          Tech Lead IA Agéntica e IA Generativa | QA Lead Automation | DevSecOps
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-cyan-400 mb-8 font-semibold" data-i18n="jose.hero.company">
          Minsait — by Indra
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="jose.hero.desc">
